{"tid":1364863,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[非打手]為大家介紹一個週末消閒的好去處","createTime":"2019-07-25T12:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T13:10:58.000Z","uid":42049,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"35f7df7007092af77ba4c0bec454396a73a06b2b","tid":1364863,"uid":42049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:49:03.000Z","msg":"近排天氣唔錯，難得到周末就當然要出街周圍行下啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港各區唔知大家行過曬未，如果未，今日就同大家推介下一個行玩食o既好去處---元朗區啦!<br />\n話說我早2個星期去過元朗，覺得嗰區環境唔錯，所以簡單做咗少少資料搜集，就share俾大家。(如果資料有少少唔準確請大家見諒)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鐘意同陽光玩遊戲o既巴絲，不妨去朗屏附近髻山行下，難度唔高，適合新手試行。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V4ST4ic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV4ST4ic.jpg&h=018927f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只需要到朗屏港鐵站A出口開始，經過朗屏邨，到風池路右轉再直行500米，一路沿山徑上山就可以直接登頂。路途短而易行，在頂峰可眺望豐樂園魚塘，大生圍以及南生圍，風光明魅。(資料來源: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/281223/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A1%8C%E5%B1%B1%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A-%E6%9C%97%E5%B1%8F%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%AB%99%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC%E7%99%BB%E9%AB%BB%E5%B1%B1-%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%BD%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D%E9%AD%9A%E5%A1%98%E6%97%A5%E8%90%BD%E9%9D%9A%E6%99%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2F281223%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%25B1%258F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2599%25BB%25E9%25AB%25BB%25E5%25B1%25B1-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25A6%25BD%25E5%258D%2597%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%259C%258D%25E9%25AD%259A%25E5%25A1%2598%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%2590%25BD%25E9%259D%259A%25E6%2599%25AF&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6ZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=24b29fcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/281223/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A1%8C%E5%B1%B1%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A-%E6%9C%97%E5%B1%8F%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%AB%99%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC%E7%99%BB%E9%AB%BB%E5%B1%B1-%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%BD%E5%8D%97%E7%94%9F%E5%9C%8D%E9%AD%9A%E5%A1%98%E6%97%A5%E8%90%BD%E9%9D%9A%E6%99%AF</a>)<br />\n<br />\n鐘意行街掃貨o既巴絲，可以到區內多間購物商場掃貨，包括:<br />\n1) YOHO<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D4q2XA9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD4q2XA9.jpg&h=fc2aed63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新落成o既YOHO，位於元朗市中心，交通方便，1、2期商場分別位於元朗港鐵站K、F出口;自己有車的話，YOHO有泊車優惠，週末電子消費滿$300可以免費泊車1小時，滿$500可以泊2小時。商場名店林立，戲院美食俱足，適合各路人士觀光購物。<br />\n2) 元朗廣場<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FOcT4gg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFOcT4gg.jpg&h=62a73bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n元朗廣場同樣位於元朗市中心，近港鐵朗屏站及輕鐵豐年路站，主打年青服飾及運動品牌，年輕至潮o既你一定要去幫襯!<br />\n3) 元朗千色滙<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RKcs8Ja.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRKcs8Ja.jpg&h=dd4af49a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n元朗千色滙位處元朗核心地段，近港鐵元朗站及輕鐵大棠路站，主打中低價市民生活所需，實為元朗街坊必去至地。<br />\n<br />\n至於鐘意食嘢打卡呃like o既你，就一定要搵元朗美食啦!<br />\n1) B仔涼粉<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2OyzOJA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2OyzOJA.jpg&h=e1afd68a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nB仔涼粉出名就係人都知啦，相信唔駛多介紹，但係佢地搬左新鋪，你地又去過未先?該店的巨型涼粉遠近馳名，最適合各位帶齊三五良朋一齊去打卡，天氣咁熱，去食下甜品消暑就最實際啦!<br />\n地址:元朗鳳琴街22號金龍樓地鋪4-5號<br />\n<br />\n2) 阿叔泰麵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xSMEZQk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxSMEZQk.png&h=0a18b6e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想食正餐的話，可以去呢間鋪食泰國船麵，據聞店主去咗泰國布吉學藝把泰國地道的味道帶到嚟元朗，D麵係佢地用30斤牛骨加入藥材熬足12個鐘先攞出嚟架，絕無味精。去唔到泰國，但係去元朗整返碗泰國船麵補數都好丫!<br />\n <br />\n地址:元朗西菁街20號益輝大廈地下3號鋪<br />\n(資料來源: <a href=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/60233/dining/%e5%85%83%e6%9c%97-%e5%b0%8f%e5%ba%97-%e7%be%8e%e9%a3%9f-%e7%85%b2%e4%bb%94%e9%a3%af-%e7%b1%b3%e8%8a%9d%e8%93%ae/6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2F60233%2Fdining%2F%25e5%2585%2583%25e6%259c%2597-%25e5%25b0%258f%25e5%25ba%2597-%25e7%25be%258e%25e9%25a3%259f-%25e7%2585%25b2%25e4%25bb%2594%25e9%25a3%25af-%25e7%25b1%25b3%25e8%258a%259d%25e8%2593%25ae%2F6%2F&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6ZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=d3acd51b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.weekendhk.com/60233/dining/%e5%85%83%e6%9c%97-%e5%b0%8f%e5%ba%97-%e7%be%8e%e9%a3%9f-%e7%85%b2%e4%bb%94%e9%a3%af-%e7%b1%b3%e8%8a%9d%e8%93%ae/6/</a>)<br />\n3) EC Kitchen<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vqNdjQt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvqNdjQt.png&h=ef453e86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至於想食小食o既巴絲，可以去呢間EC Kitchen度試食佢地的漢堡，佢地o既豪華漢堡有齊海膽、黑松露、手打牛肉、芝士，d牛肉大大份，色香味俱全，淨係買嚟打卡都抵啦!<br />\n <br />\n地址: 元朗鳳攸南街3號好順景大廈二座19號鋪<br />\n(資料來源: <a href=\"http://www.coco01.today/post/504206\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coco01.today%2Fpost%2F504206&d=5pfOjvQv%2F9K29PXjFwfL6ZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=a9738a43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.coco01.today/post/504206</a>)<br />\n<br />\n去到元朗仲有手信買添呀!<br />\n恒香老餅家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bixkKhf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbixkKhf.png&h=0a20b755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恒香老餅家1920年成立，佢地的總店就喺元朗，恒香中式糕餅口碑極好，尤其是傳統手製老婆餅，啱哂一家大小一齊品嘗，去完元朗就當然要買返d返屋企同屋企人一齊分享下元朗o既味道啦!<br />\n地址:元朗大馬路66號(近元朗港鐵站B出口)<br />\n<br />\n今個週末得閒o既巴絲冇嘢做的話，不妨到元朗行個大運啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟行街，各適其式</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位仲有咩好去處提議呢?"},{"pid":"b32df0f19d709329c5e4e564dcfac78071613dee","tid":1364863,"uid":118125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:52:38.000Z","msg":"元朗反黑遊行因為警察害怕黑社會而取消了<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>李鵬悼念會</strong></span>在元朗舉行<br />\n毌忘李同志遺願:<br />\n1. 撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定義<br />\n3. 撤回所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會，追究警黑勾結、濫權<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTbYvJD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTbYvJD.png&h=655c15f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n*完成悼念後可以各自在元朗大馬路購物、品嚐元朗美食*<br />\n溫馨提示：可以在元朗站乘搭交通工具離開元朗市"},{"pid":"1ad7e27488b9c71987c26c9798d0bc2aa926ae41","tid":1364863,"uid":42049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:53:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9ec0336ab2291b20a36462ca5f12508f62c999","tid":1364863,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:53:41.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1de8034302e8016e9d833557faccc45db437c5f9","tid":1364863,"uid":42049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b32df0f19d709329c5e4e564dcfac78071613dee","tid":1364863,"uid":118125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:52:38.000Z","msg":"元朗反黑遊行因為警察害怕黑社會而取消了<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>李鵬悼念會</strong></span>在元朗舉行<br />\n毌忘李同志遺願:<br />\n1. 撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定義<br />\n3. 撤回所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會，追究警黑勾結、濫權<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTbYvJD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTbYvJD.png&h=655c15f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n*完成悼念後可以各自在元朗大馬路購物、品嚐元朗美食*<br />\n溫馨提示：可以在元朗站乘搭交通工具離開元朗市"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:54:13.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打補充"},{"pid":"81da55c706d4aa64787f75deb0fdfbb7086ccabf","tid":1364863,"